1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,200
What if the rain falling on you was more acidic than battery acid?

2
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:11,600
Sulfur and nitrogen oxides, released from factories and cars, mix with water vapor, creating acid rain.

3
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:16,400
This rain can harm plants, fish, and even the structures we build.

4
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:18,000
But there's good news!

5
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:21,600
Regulations have significantly reduced these emissions in many regions.

6
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:25,600
Research shows ecosystems are bouncing back, thanks to these efforts.

7
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:30,000
Want to learn more about how we can protect our planet?

8
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:31,200
Follow for more!
